type: web_research
title: 暗号通貨Dual Investment API仕様 総合調査結果
key_insights[8]: "Binance: /sapi/v1/dci/ 配下に専用Dual Investment APIあり (product/list, product/subscribe, product/positions, product/accounts, auto_compound/edit-status)","Bitget: Dual Investment専用APIは公開されていない。Earn API V2 (savings/sharkfin) + Spot Trade APIで代替実装が必要","Bybit: /v5/earn/ 配下に統合Earn APIあり (product, place-order, order, position, yield)。Dual Asset専用APIの確認は公式ドキュメント要参照","OKX: /api/v5/finance/staking-defi/ と /api/v5/finance/savings/ あり。Dual Investment専用APIは確認できず","CCXT: Earn/Dual Investment統一メソッドは未実装。implicitAPI経由で直接エンドポイント呼び出しが必要","tiagosiebler SDKs: bitget-api, bybit-api, okx-api すべてEarn系エンドポイントのラッパーメソッドを提供","認証: Bitget=HMAC-SHA256+Base64 (ACCESS-KEY/SIGN/PASSPHRASE/TIMESTAMP), Binance=HMAC-SHA256, OKX=同様, Bybit=同様","テストネット: Bitget=同URL+paptrading:1ヘッダー, Binance=testnet.binance.vision, Bybit=api-testnet.bybit.com, OKX=同URL+x-simulated-trading:1"
findings[12]: "Binance Dual Investment API endpoints: GET /sapi/v1/dci/product/list, POST /sapi/v1/dci/product/subscribe, GET /sapi/v1/dci/product/positions, GET /sapi/v1/dci/product/accounts, POST /sapi/v1/dci/product/auto_compound/edit-status","Binance response fields: id, investCoin, exercisedCoin, strikePrice, duration, settleDate, purchaseDecimal, purchaseEndTime, canPurchase, apr, orderId, minAmount, maxAmount, optionType (PUT/CALL), isAutoCompoundEnable, autoCompoundPlanList","Binance autoCompoundPlan values: STANDARD, ADVANCED, None","Bitget Earn Savings: /api/v2/earn/savings/product|account|assets|records|subscribe-info|subscribe|subscribe-result|redeem|redeem-result","Bitget Earn Sharkfin: /api/v2/earn/sharkfin/product|account|assets|records|subscribe-info|subscribe|subscribe-result","Bitget Earn Loan: /api/v2/earn/loan/public/coinInfos|borrow|ongoing-orders|repay etc.","Bybit Earn: /v5/earn/product|place-order|order|position|yield|hourly-yield","OKX Staking-DeFi: /api/v5/finance/staking-defi/offers|purchase|redeem|cancel|orders-active|orders-history","OKX Savings: /api/v5/finance/savings/balance|purchase-redempt|set-lending-rate|lending-history","OKX ETH Staking: /api/v5/finance/staking-defi/eth/product-info|purchase|redeem|balance","Rate limits: Bitget=20req/s public, 10req/s trade; Binance=6000 weight/min IP-based; Bybit=per-second per-UID; OKX=endpoint-specific","WebSocket: Bitget=240sub/hr/conn, max 1000ch, 10msg/s; Bitget demo WS=wss://wspap.bitget.com/v2/ws/"
refs[9]: "Binance DI: developers.binance.com/docs/dual_investment","Bitget Earn: bitget.com/api-doc/earn/savings/Savings-Products","Bitget Sharkfin: bitget.com/api-doc/earn/sharkfin/Shark-Products","Bitget Auth: bitget.com/api-doc/common/signature","Bybit V5: bybit-exchange.github.io/docs/v5/intro","OKX V5: okx.com/docs-v5/en/","tiagosiebler/bitget-api: github.com/tiagosiebler/bitget-api","tiagosiebler/bybit-api: github.com/tiagosiebler/bybit-api","tiagosiebler/okx-api: github.com/tiagosiebler/okx-api"
recommendations[4]: Binanceを最優先で実装（唯一の専用Dual Investment API提供）,Bitgetはearn/savings+spot/tradeの組み合わせでDual Investment模倣実装,"tiagosiebler SDKs (bitget-api, bybit-api, okx-api) をNode.js実装で活用",CCXTはDual Investment非対応のためimplicitAPI経由かSDK直接利用推奨
